{"tid":2357512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(瓏門）譚惠珠：初選本身不是非法　關鍵在參選人表明阻撓政府","createTime":"2021-01-07T12:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T14:44:11.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"974094dcd698c19005a7bf56b540b3afd4f33dab","tid":2357512,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"警方昨日（6日）大舉拘捕53名民主派人士，指他們組織或參與去年7月的民主派初選，涉嫌違反《港區國安法》中的「顛覆國家政權罪」，大部分被捕人士被通宵扣查至今。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠今日（7日）接受電視台訪問時表示，初選本身並不是非法行動，關鍵在於發起人戴耀廷提倡的「攬炒十步曲」，以及參選人以簽署或公開承諾形式，表明會否決《財政預算案》，嚴重阻撓政府依法履行職能。"},{"pid":"a7ed67d9988b1ef165c35c7ff27c7717d74b1e35","tid":2357512,"uid":14494,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"咁不如宣誓果陣加埋唔可以反對政府議案 唔可以持相反意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a3e7c1f75d369ad77d33bc88b7adf9699aa194","tid":2357512,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"思想犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc0ab44b404d19b8a09fe7bc3b5b3787b5a37cf","tid":2357512,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"呢件object堅冇理由唔畀人放入sanction list"},{"pid":"745c34d20c5a4d3954498188c19f18dc2f102f84","tid":2357512,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tam-01_sWwOG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftam-01_sWwOG_1200x0.png&h=77fed2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老牌漢奸譚穢豬"},{"pid":"d5ce0dca83e5e6d77e2064fa25d686e631583fa6","tid":2357512,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"745c34d20c5a4d3954498188c19f18dc2f102f84","tid":2357512,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"